  <p id="NA1b7P">The <a href="https://www.theverge.com/23687731/pixel-hardware-rumors-7a-foldable-fold-tablet">rumors are true</a>: next week, Google will introduce its first foldable phone, <a href="https://store.google.com/intl/en/ideas/pixel-is-open/">the Pixel Fold</a>, during the Google I/O 2023 event. </p>
